                <note rend="inline" type="source">819.52G31/5: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Panama</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Flexer</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-05-21T14:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 21, 1938—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>20. Your 35, May 19, 2 p.m. The War and Navy Departments are telegraphing to the
                    Commanding General and to the Commandant of the Fifteenth Naval District to
                    consult with the Legation and to investigate the reported transaction. Please
                    inform the Department promptly by telegram regarding all developments.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
